 Nuss","competitor_type":"individual","additional_course":false,"affiliation_labels":["COC"]},{"metrics":[],"team_id":null,"result_id":"019d0f4d-7e2b-72ad-aec9-90e14ea6c033","time_text":null,"competitive":true,"course_rank":null,"status_code":"OK","affiliations":[{"label":"COC"}],"outcome_text":"OK","overall_rank":56,"result_notes":null,"category_name":"24 C 24 Pts Time limit 75 minutes","category_rank":28,"individual_id":"019b7fed-a88a-7e76-b17a-062d4b2ada0c","metric_summary":null,"competitor_name":"Rolf Kuestner","competitor_type":"individual","additional_course":false,"affiliation_labels":["COC"]}],"course_id":"019d0f4d-7e57-7ab2-a2ac-b25b8ef9210a","course_name":"Score-O","distance_km":null,"result_count":56,"control_count":null,"course_climb_m":null}],"event_id":"019b81f3-1f4d-7e1c-9375-4789231c0f54","venue_id":"019b81f3-1f39-7e1d-afe3-ae19e64bef48","event_date":"2017-09-10","event_kind":"race","event_name":"Choose Your Adventure #3: Campus!","venue_name":"South Seattle College","event_notes":null,"course_count":1,"event_status":null,"result_count":56,"citation_count":3,"event_comments":"The Choose Your Adventure series is designed to be extra fun, social, and friendly for beginners, yet interesting for seasoned veterans.\nAt Choose Your Adventure events, everyone gets the same map with checkpoints marked all over it. Then, after a mass start, you can find as many checkpoints as you want, in whichever order you want! Just be sure to mind the time, since there’s also a time limit. Return to the finish on-time, or lose precious points for every minute you’re late. (Wear a watch!)\nChoose Your Adventure is especially good for beginners, since if you can’t find a checkpoint, you can just skip it and keep going. Veterans are challenged by trying to identify the most efficient route to find all the checkpoints, and the mass start means head-to-head racing for some.\nThanks to the excitement-inducing time limit, everyone finishes around the same time, making post-event socializing a core feature of Choose Your Adventure events.\nIs this your first event or do you want to improve your skills? Meet us from 12:00pm – 1:00pm for up to an hour of free skills instruction!\nThis event is being held at the same location immediately after the Seattle Adventure Running Tournament. If you aren’t participating in the tournament, you are invited to arrive early and watch the semifinals and finals beforehand!\nCheck back later for special notes from the Course Designer(s).","external_links":[{"link_url":"https://goo.gl/maps/37T8HsK2x2z","link_type":"directions"},{"link_url":"https://cascadeoc.org/event/campusadventure/","link_type":"event_page"},{"link_url":"https://cascadeoc.org/map/south-seattle-college/","link_type":"map"},{"link_url":"https://cascadeoc.org/result/2193/","link_type":"related_result"},{"link_url":"https://cascadeoc.org/result/choose-adventure-2-whidbey/","link_type":"related_result"},{"link_url":"http://rg.cascadeoc.org/rg2/#191","link_type":"routegadget"},{"link_url":"https://cascadeoc.org/series/adventure/","link_type":"series"}],"volunteer_roles":[{"role_name":"Course Designer","individual_id":"019d0a11-4d30-76bd-9f88-296000621d49","citation_count":1,"individual_name":"Patrick Nuss","volunteer_hours":null,"volunteer_points":null},{"role_name":"Epunch Coordinator","individual_id":"019d0a11-4d2f-736d-863f-5e546e61e969","citation_count":1,"individual_name":"Ing Uhlin","volunteer_hours":null,"volunteer_points":null},{"role_name":"Meet Director","individual_id":"019d0a11-4d30-76bd-9f88-296000621d49","citation_count":1,"individual_name":"Patrick Nuss","volunteer_hours":null,"volunteer_points":null}],"organizing_club_id":"01912f3e-e3e1-7e8e-b3c6-32387a8b4990","result_source_brief":"CascadeOC Website: https://www.cascadeoc.org/result/choose-your-adventure-3-campus/","organizing_club_name":"Cascade Orienteering Club"}
